title: 820-3330 fan turn but nothing more
message: Yeah this is not looking good. Check resistance between pin 2 of the PPBUS fuse and CPU Vcore. If it's low, this is probably trash.

title: 820-3330 fan turn but nothing more
message:
No pulse at all at L7510/20/30?
Any drop pulse at pin48 of U7400?

title: 820-3330 fan turn but nothing more
message: No CPU Vcore is bad :( Check U7400 area for corrosion. Any history on this board?

title: 820-3330 fan turn but nothing more
message:
PPBUS fuse = 320Kohm
CPU VCORE = 1,2ohm
No pulse at all at L7510/20/30, nothing
pin48 of U7400 = 1,05V
No corrosion, very clean board. is it GPU?

title: 820-3330 fan turn but nothing more
message: No it is not the GPU there is no Vcore. You ca try another BIOS, but after that it is probably a bad CPU/PCH.
